# Reference Documentation

## Primary Repositories

Always refer to these before implementing BIM/IFC features:

1. **That Open Engine** — https://github.com/ThatOpen
   - `engine_components` → `@thatopen/components`, `@thatopen/components-front`
   - `engine_web-ifc` → `web-ifc` (WASM IFC parser)
   - `engine_fragment` → `@thatopen/fragments` (tile-based rendering)
   - Docs: https://docs.thatopen.com/
   - Examples: https://github.com/ThatOpen/engine_components/tree/main/packages/core/src/fragments

2. **buildingSMART Community** — https://github.com/buildingsmart-community
   - `Community-Sample-Test-Files` → IFC/BCF/IDS test files
   - `ifcJSON` → IFC.JSON specification
   - Standards reference: https://standards.buildingsmart.org/

3. **IfcOpenShell** — https://github.com/IfcOpenShell/IfcOpenShell
   - `ifcopenshell-python` → Python library for IFC parsing (used by backend)
   - `ifcconvert` → CLI to convert IFC to other formats
   - `ifctester` → IDS model auditing
   - `ifcclash` → Clash detection
   - `ifcdiff` → Compare changes between IFC models
   - `ifccsv` → Export/import schedules from IFC
   - Supports: IFC2x3, IFC4, IFC4x1, IFC4x2, IFC4x3
   - Docs: https://docs.ifcopenshell.org/
   - Bonsai (Blender BIM): https://bonsaibim.org/

## Test Files Source

- Official: https://github.com/buildingSMART/Sample-Test-Files (IFC4, IFC4x3)
- Community: https://github.com/buildingsmart-community/Community-Sample-Test-Files (IFC2x3, Git LFS)
- Local: `TestIFC/` folder in project root
